title: SANTANA MERRIWEATHER POST PAVILION COLUMBIA AUGUST 16, 1973
description:
SANTANA
MERRIWEATHER POST PAVILION
COLUMBIA, 
MD
AUGUST 16, 1973

SBD

This is the second of 2 Columbia shows in this year.
The first one, in March in South Carolina, will be posted later

Has this ever been shared before here? Couldn't find it in the Dime Bot that went back to 2006.
Even if it were a reseed, still very very much worth the grab!
What a fantastice sound and performance!!!
Outstanding tracks: Yours is the light, Samba de Sausalito, Flor de Canela (an early version from 
the Borboletta tune). But the rest is actually just as as good.

Enjoy another 73 Santana gem!!
